%%{init: { 'theme': 'default', 'themeVariables': { 'background': '#f8fafc', 'primaryColor': '#e0f2fe', 'lineColor': '#475569' }}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    
    actor U as Traveler Browser (React)
    participant N as Nginx Proxy
    participant R as FastAPI Router
    participant A as AuthX Middleware
    participant B as Backend Service
    participant DB as PostgreSQL DB

    Note over U, R: Faza 1: Cerere esuata (Access Token expirat)
    U->>N: Fetch: GET /api/protected-route (Authorization Bearer)
    N->>R: Proxy Pass catre FastAPI
    R->>A: Trigger Depends(access_token_header)
    A->>A: Validare esuata: Token Expirat
    A-->>R: Returneaza 401 Unauthorized
    R-->>N: HTTP 401 Response
    N-->>U: HTTP 401 Unauthorized

    Note over U, DB: Faza 2: Interceptare 401 si Mecanism Silent Refresh
    U->>N: Fetch: POST /api/auth/refresh (HttpOnly Cookie present)
    N->>R: Proxy Pass catre FastAPI
    R->>A: Apeleaza refresh_token_cookie(request)
    A->>A: Extrage si verifica Refresh Token din Cookie
    A->>DB: Interogare is_token_revoked(token)
    activate DB
    DB-->>A: Token valid (Nu este revocat in Blacklist)
    deactivate DB
    A->>DB: Inserare token vechi in BlacklistToken (Revocare)
    A->>A: Genereaza noul Access Token & noul Refresh Token
    A-->>R: Returneaza noile acreditari
    R-->>N: HTTP 200 OK (New Tokens)
    N-->>U: Salveaza noul Access Token in localStorage

    Note over U, B: Faza 3: Re-trimitere automata cerere initiala (Retry)
    U->>N: GET /api/protected-route (Authorization Bearer NOU)
    N->>R: Proxy Pass catre FastAPI
    R->>A: Trigger Depends(access_token_header)
    A->>A: Validare succes: Token valid
    A-->>R: Returneaza TokenPayload (user_id)
    R->>B: Executa endpoint (Ex: chat, itinerary, sessions)
    activate B
    B->>DB: Validare Ownership Resursa (owner_id == user_id)
    activate DB
    DB-->>B: Confirmare drepturi de acces
    deactivate DB
    B-->>R: Returneaza datele solicitate din subsistem
    deactivate B
    R-->>N: HTTP 200 OK (JSON Data)
    N-->>U: HTTP 200 OK (Datele sunt afisate in UI)